93
00:04:57,790 --> 00:04:58,940
Where is your father?

94
00:04:59,110 --> 00:05:00,349
Didn't he come with you?

95
00:05:00,350 --> 00:05:01,820
Did you call him?

96
00:05:01,990 --> 00:05:03,140
Isn't he here with you?

97
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:03,669
He...

98
00:05:03,670 --> 00:05:05,580
There's a huge fire
at San Po Kong today.

99
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:08,050
My father is going to fight a fire
so he can't be here.

100
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,410
See?

101
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:12,719
He asked me to buy

102
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,460
Sesame Glutinous Rice Balls for you.

103
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:16,780
That's better, at least.

104
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,850
Have a sip of ginger tea.

105
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,050
Is it nice?

106
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,460
Mom,

107
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,050
