108
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,090
I've been very busy lately.

109
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:35,610
No matter what,

110
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,050
promise me

111
00:05:37,350 --> 00:05:38,530
not to simply throw a tantrum

112
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:39,479
and eat well.

113
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,260
All right?

114
00:05:43,550 --> 00:05:44,460
Have one.

115
00:05:49,550 --> 00:05:50,580
Ming.

116
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:53,290
Where is your father?

117
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:55,020
Isn't he here with you today?

118
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,429
When is he coming?

119
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:59,610
Have a glutinous rice ball first.
Eat this first and I'll tell you, all right?

120
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,229
Does everyone

121
