play with their phones nowadays?

122
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,040
Will you die
if you don't play with your phones?

123
00:06:33,110 --> 00:06:34,109
Shouldn't we talk

124
00:06:34,110 --> 00:06:35,490
when we are eating?

125
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,940
- Are you talking about me?
- Yes.

126
00:06:38,670 --> 00:06:40,519
What else can I talk about
with you besides work?

127
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,399
Not really.

128
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,850
We have many things to talk about.

129
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:44,869
For example. Are you in a relationship?

130
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,650
- What does it have to do with you?
- You're right.

131
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:47,839
You're a tomboy.

132
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:50,109
I'm sure no one is pursuing you.
Asking you is a waste of time.

133
00:06:50,110 --> 00:06:51,279
You have such a foul mouth.

134
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,549
No woman will like you.

135
00:06:52,550 --> 00:06:53,820
You are wrong.

136
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,959
I have a wife

137
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:55,749
and a daughter.

138
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,189
It's a happy family of three.

139
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,020
Really?

140
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,749
You believe everything I say.

141
00:06:59,750 --> 00:07:00,970
