143
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:06,700
Whether I become a police officer
or not is none of your business.

144
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,900
- I don't want you to be lied to.
- Just drink your tea.

145
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:13,020
Don't trust people so easily.

146
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:13,839
Dr. Zhou.

147
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,460
Sorry for being late.

148
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:16,780
