164
00:07:41,110 --> 00:07:42,309
What is HAB?

165
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,039
HAB is

166
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,519
Hostile Attribution Bias.

167
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,789
They think everyone in the world

168
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:46,839
is against them.

169
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,309
So, they have a strong urge

170
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:49,340
to get revenge.

171
00:07:52,990 --> 00:07:54,669
Back then, his mother was the one

172
00:07:54,670 --> 00:07:56,700
who accused him in court.

173
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,610
Later, he was locked up in an asylum.

174
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,780
Who will he take revenge on?

175
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:08,960
(Investigation Report, Mai Xiaojuan)
According to Mai Xiaojuan's colleague,

176
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:09,959
four days before the murder,

177
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:12,569
Mai Xiaojuan suddenly took a day off
and said she was bringing his daughter

178
00:08:12,569 --> 00:08:13,960
to Mainland China
to visit their relatives.

179
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,580
We checked with
the Immigration Department.

180
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:17,610
There were no records of her
and her daughter leaving the borders.

181
00:08:18,350 --> 00:08:18,989
Can we trace

182
00:08:18,990 --> 00:08:20,140
her phone signal?

183
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,170
On the day Mai Xiaojuan disappeared,

184
00:08:25,350 --> 00:08:26,650
she went to more than 10 places.

185
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,719
She went to every district

186
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,650
in Hong Kong, China.

187
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,020
It was extremely abnormal.

188
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:32,159
What is her last location

189
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:33,180
on her phone?

190
00:08:33,590 --> 00:08:35,850
Lai Chi Kok
Cheung Fat Industrial Building.

191
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:40,130
Footage of the streets
around the building are all here.

192
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:49,999
Hello.

193
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:50,970
Hello. Police.

194
00:08:51,107 --> 00:08:52,279
I need to check your camera footage.

195
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,239
Please cooperate with us.

196
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:53,709
Police.

197
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:54,580
This way.

198
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,309
Have you seen this person?

199
00:08:56,310 --> 00:08:57,250
No.

200
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:57,879
All right.

201
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,399
Contact us if you have anything.

202
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,180
All right.

203
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,300
I'm full.

204
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,940
Where are you going?

205
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:33,660
Work.

206
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:38,420
Investigating a case with your brains.

207
00:09:38,950 --> 00:09:40,090
If you use a computer,

208
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:42,060
your eyes will go blind sooner or later.

209
00:09:47,310 --> 00:09:49,549
(Mai Zhihong's sister
disappeared on the same day)

210
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,970
(as his mother's funeral.)

211
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,159
(He will never miss)

212
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,660
(such a good opportunity for revenge.)

213
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:54,639
(Mai Zhihong is crazy)

214
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,660
(but he's not stupid.)

215
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:57,469
(He must have a detailed plan.)

216
00:09:57,470 --> 00:09:59,603
(Funeral Hall)

217
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,940
Hello. Police.

218
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:04,669
What is it?

219
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:05,639
I want to ask

220
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,090
if you've seen this person before.

221
00:10:08,950 --> 00:10:09,890
No.

222
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:12,540
His mother's funeral
was here a few days ago.

223
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:13,589
He might come here.

224
00:10:13,590 --> 00:10:15,130
See carefully and see if you remember.

225
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:17,770
Officer,

226
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,069
many filial people

227
00:10:19,070 --> 00:10:20,239
come here every day.

228
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,060
I really don't remember.

229
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,879
His mother was Luo Qiuyan.

230
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:25,639
Her funeral

231
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:27,220
was here a few days ago.

232
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,589
Can you see which colleague of yours

233
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:30,090
is in charge of this funeral hall?

234
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,130
Hui!

235
00:10:36,830 --> 00:10:37,730
What is it?

236
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:39,639
A few days ago,

237
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,220
Luo Qiuyan had her funeral here.

238
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,949
- Were you in charge of the funeral hall?
- I was.

239
00:10:42,950 --> 00:10:43,890
What is it?

240
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,180
Do you recognise this person?

241
00:10:45,470 --> 00:10:46,829
This man was acting strange.

242
00:10:46,830 --> 00:10:47,879
I remember he brought

243
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:48,673
a funeral spray here.

244
00:10:48,674 --> 00:10:52,295
(Unfilial Son Zhihong)

245
00:10:52,296 --> 00:10:59,330
(Unfilial Son Zhihong, Mother's Funeral)

246
00:11:07,441 --> 00:11:09,380
(Unfilial Son Zhihong, Mother's Funeral)

247
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:11,919
I still can't

248
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,300
meet Mother one last time.

249
00:11:14,590 --> 00:11:15,420
Hello.

250
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:16,850
Sister.

251
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,700
How did you come out?

252
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,159
Mom came to me in my dreams

253
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,399
and said she wanted to see me.

254
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,879
Mom didn't want to see you at all!

255
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,060
You jinx!

256
00:11:26,470 --> 00:11:27,789
Don't be so rude.

257
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:28,789
You're so loud.

258
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:31,460
Don't say this in front of your daughter.
You are setting a bad example.

259
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,180
However,

260
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:36,220
my niece is really cute.

261
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:39,970
Hello, Siti.

262
00:11:40,430 --> 00:11:41,490
Hello, Madam.

263
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:42,829
Sorry.

264
00:11:42,830 --> 00:11:43,820
What's wrong?

265
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,770
Qiao is missing.

266
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:47,340
What do you mean she's missing?

267
00:11:47,430 --> 00:11:49,130
Didn't I ask you
to pick her up at school?

268
00:11:49,224 --> 00:11:50,644
Didn't you watch over her?

269
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,279
After she answered the call,

270
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,189
her face turned pale

271
00:11:54,190 --> 00:11:55,460
and left in a taxi.

272
00:11:55,670 --> 00:11:56,420
Thank you.

273
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:57,660
Hello.

274
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:59,189
Before Mai Xiaojuan went missing,

275
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:00,709
she hailed a ride
in front of the funeral hall.

276
00:12:00,710 --> 00:12:01,159
Check and see

277
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,279
which taxi station's taxi it was.

278
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,420
Taxi station?

279
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,239
Everyone is using

280
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,370
ride-hailing applications now.

281
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:07,940
Can you find it?

282
00:12:09,430 --> 00:12:11,220
